cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.HC 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques to analyze user reviews of Android apps. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques to extract relevant information from the reviews, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another likely category. The use of machine learning models for classification and prediction makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) a possible category. The study also involves human-computer interaction (HCI) as it deals with user feedback and app ratings, which makes cs.CY (Computers and Society) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves data analysis and statistics, which makes cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) another possible category.
